reviewText: There's alot of criticism for low budget movies.., This particular movie is the "break through" kind, The casting was a blockbuster assemble of young & seasoned actors, they pulled the (typical)script thru no matter how large or small the parts were.., The sound & lighting was B+.., The scenes weren't "Hangover Dvd" funny, But this ran a close 2nd place... Definitely a Dvd you'd pull out the collection to entertain friends...
